――The complicated discussion in the large chamber was approaching a temporary conclusion.

???: [To be frank, the situation had been vastly different from what we had expected at the start. However, I can say that having been able to avoid the fall of the Fortress City and acquire the cooperation of General Yorna are definite good results]

