With fluffy hair and those wide eyes, he looked over the faces of everyone in the large chamber. To Zikr's words, Emilia nodded and said "Yes, that's right.]

Emilia: [Some disheartening things also happened, but the fact that everyone is gathered here is because we did our best. This time, let's rely on that and make everyone's goals come true.]

