???: [One last point, is it? ...I do not feel very good about it if it will be a continuation of our discussion a moment ago]

Seeing Zikr's single raised finger as he nodded at Emilia's words, Otto grumbled as his cheeks twitched.

"Indeed," Zikr continued, as if to bolster Otto's bad premonition.

Zikr: [This would be a continuation of the previous discussion. This discussion also involves Miss Natsumi, who is being treated like the black-haired crown prince]

